{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:00:02.606Z","taskId":"KB-002","text":" spec being reviewed.\n\n4. **No actual automated tests** — Step 8 is titled \"Testing & Verification\" but contains no automated test suites. It's all manual verification (build, lint, format check, dev server check). For a scaffolding task, this is reasonable — there's no application logic to test. But the review criteria asks about \"real automated tests with assertions\" — there genuinely","type":"thinking","agent":"reviewer"}
